com.tencent.cos.xml.transfer

类 MultipartUploadHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tencent.cos.xml.transfer.MultipartUploadHelper

  • public class MultipartUploadHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    MultipartUploadHelper封装了底层分片上传的相关接口，给您提供了更加方便的分片上传方法。 分片上传文件 
    
 MultipartUploadHelper helper = new MultipartUploadHelper(cosXmlService);
 helper.setBucket(bucketName);
 helper.setCosPath(cosPath); // 需要以 '/' 开头
 helper.setSrcPath(srcPath); // 本地文件路径
 helper.setProgressListener(new QCloudProgressListener() {

   public void onProgress(long progress, long total) {
     Log.d("TAG", "progress is " + progress + ", total is " + total);
   }
 });

 helper.upload();
    暂停和恢复分片上传 
    
 // 暂停任务
 ResumeData resumeData = helper.cancel();

 // 恢复任务
 CosXmlResult cosXmlResult = helper.resume(resumeData);

 // 删除任务
 AbortMultiUploadResult abortMultiUploadResult = helper.abort();
    另请参阅:
    CosXml.initMultipartUpload(InitMultipartUploadRequest), CosXml.uploadPart(UploadPartRequest), CosXml.listMultiUploads(ListMultiUploadsRequest), CosXml.completeMultiUpload(CompleteMultiUploadRequest), CosXml.abortMultiUpload(AbortMultiUploadRequest)
